{"tid":1563850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋人","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T14:41:02.000Z","uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"43cf9f373ef4919137a0a9cc5aaf425e68ab0a22","tid":1563850,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"自從9月1，有好多報稱無可疑既自殺.無記錯已經超過10個.但呢個數字只係已知數字...<br />\n<br />\n我想問下大家有冇發覺有身邊既人突然消失？包括由6月開始.其實唔排除會搵到越黎越多自殺咗既失蹤人口.<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果你知道朋友被拉都請確認一下佢地係唔係安好.<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一有發現多口問一句.因為家人入手應該無乜可能，但佢地走/失蹤前理論上應該有聯絡過朋友/同學/同事.希望大家可以行多一步，多口問一句！<br />\n<br />\n因為呢一方面唔會有任何渠道/人可以幫到我地.<br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少！"},{"pid":"a3e6f4e465da1c09ed68d175ddd176b92c868a80","tid":1563850,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"61d48742f9d5d17a4977ab56a2e1d5711ef4697a","tid":1563850,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:23:46.000Z","msg":"[文長][中期檢討]希望大家入黎睇下我地現有既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563440/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"850357a15ecf413b570274cf8d9272ee872d2c61","tid":1563850,"uid":91666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":